faqList.title: What does “Scan” mean?

answerList.title: What does “Scan” mean?
answerList.description: Use the Scan function, to complete an artificial intelligence (AI) scan of a vehicle to detect damages. Go to "Work Orders" and select the work order. Click "Scan" in the bottom right corner. Read the instructions and press "Next". Toggle the button next to each item to choose which photos to include in the scan. Exterior of Vehicle photos are required. Click "Next" to load the AI inspection. Read the instructions and click "Next". Tap on the screen to add the corresponding image, then click "Next". Repeat this process until all photos have been uploaded. On the final photo screen, click "Finish" to submit the inspection for review.
